 terms  conditions privacy policy about us  localshares about us management nashville  its companies fund list investor materials fund summary fund holdings premium discount chart about etfs news contact   localshares™ offers the first investment product of its kind based on a breakthrough economic development strategy   the citybased exchange traded fund etf localshares investments llc provides financial services products to enable investors to participate in the potential of geographic locations such as american cities as demonstrated by the publiclytraded companies that surround them localshares investments llc establishes exchange traded funds etfs that include equities based within certain targeted regional markets the nashville area etf launched in  is the company’s first citybased etf and includes publiclytraded companies based in and around nashville tennessee localshares investments llc was founded in    sei investments distribution co  freedom valley drive oaks pa  is the distributor for the nashville area etf check the background of sidco on finras brokercheck an active secondary market for the funds shares may not exist although the funds shares will be listed on an exchange subject to notice of issuance it is possible that an active trading market may not develop or be maintained all etf products are subject to risk which may result in the loss of principal investment in smaller companies typically exhibit higher volatility the fund will invest substantially all of its assets in the securities of companies that have their headquarters or principal place of business located in the nashville tennessee region the fund may be impacted by events or conditions affecting the region to a greater extent than a fund that did not focus its investments in that manner the fund is expected to invest a relatively large percentage of its assets in the healthcare sector and negative performance of the sector will negatively impact the fund diversification may not protect against investment loss carefully consider the nashville area etf’s investment objective risk factors and charges and expenses before investing this and other important information can be found in the nashville area etf’s prospectus which may be obtained by calling nash  read it carefully before investing etf shares are not redeemable with the issuing fund other than in large creation unit aggregations instead investors must buy or sell etf shares in the secondary market with the assistance of a stockbroker in doing so the investor may incur brokerage commissions and may pay more than net asset value when buying and receive less than net asset value when selling sei investments distribution co is not affiliated with localshares investments llc not fdic insured  no bank guarantee  may lose money   management  margaret o dolan president knowledge division michael schulz director of marketing localshares investments llc board of directors  elizabeth seigenthaler courtney localshares investment trust board  elizabeth seigenthaler courtney doug cruickshanks craven crowell rebecca stillwell   localshares     harding pike    ste     nashville tn     nash     infolocalsharescom site map  printable view      localshares all rights reserved localshares investment trust  nashville area etf arcanash  fundamentals analysis loading user profile paid plan pricing  nothing to display profile support learning about logout dashboard sign up login localshares investment trust  nashville area etf arcanash snowflake description no noteworthy features the snowflake is generated from  checks in  different areas read more below nash arca m market cap add to portfolio asset management and custody banks company description localshares investment trust  nashville area etf is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by localshares inc more info add to portfolio compare print invest warning this is a fund or etf currently our data availability for these is poor we only recommend using the